title: The Limit - Trickiest Tunnel (Extension of the Jubilee Line)
description:
The Limit - Trickiest Tunnel (Extension of the Jubilee Line)

Hugh Doherty has spent a lifetime building tunnels, from the Clyde River Tunnel to the Hong Kong Mass Transit System. But now he is facing his biggest challenge yet - to build a new tube line under the heart of London, in record time.

To speed up the job he is using a spray-on, rapid setting concrete lining, but as another tunnel using the same method collapses, the work grinds to a halt. When his two trusted tunnelling machines then break down, it seems his quest may be doomed.

Narrated by Robbie Coltrane.

First shown: BBC, 28 Nov 1995
Duration: 29 minutes
